1. e4 {Marin,Mihail Marin,Mihail Marin,Mihail Marin,Mihail: 'Marin,M'} c6 2. d4 d5 3. exd5 cxd5 4. Bd3 Nc6 5. c3 Qc7 6. h3 e6 7. Nf3 Bd6 8. O-O Nge7 9. a4 Bd7 10. Na3 a6 11. Re1 f6 (11... O-O 12. Bd2 f6 13. c4 Bxa3 14. Rxa3 dxc4 15. Bxc4 Nxd4 16. Rc3 Nxf3+ 17. Qxf3 Nc6) 12. c4 Nb4 {A very rare move, which seems to be not bad at all, at least in view of this game. Marin,Mihail: 'Marin,M: 'A very rare move, which seems to be not bad at all, at least in view of this game.'' Marin,Mihail: 'A very rare move, which seems to be not bad at all, at least in view of this game.'} 13. c5 Bf4 14. Bf1 Bxc1 15. Qxc1 O-O 16. Qd2 Nec6 17. Nb5 axb5 18. axb5 Rxa1 19. Rxa1 Nxd4 {Despite the apparent positional concessions, Black's queenside position is very hard to crack. At the same time, his attack on the other wing is ready to start. Marin,Mihail: 'Marin,M: 'Despite the apparent positional concessions, Black's queenside position is very hard to crack. At the same time, his attack on the other wing is ready to start.'' Marin,Mihail: 'Despite the apparent positional concessions, Black's queenside position is very hard to crack. At the same time, his attack on the other wing is ready to start. '} 20. Nxd4 Qxc5 21. Ra4 Na6 22. bxa6 Bxa4 {Allowing the opening of the queenside. Marin,Mihail: 'Marin,M: 'Allowing the opening of the queenside.'' Marin,Mihail: 'Allowing the opening of the queenside.'} 23. Nxe6 Qd6 24. Nxf8 bxa6 25. Nxh7 $44 Kxh7 26. Qd3+ Kh6 27. Qxa6 Qb4 28. Qa8 Bc2 29. Qh8+ $5 Kg6 30. Qe8+ Kh6 31. Qe3+ g5 32. Qc3 Qxc3 33. bxc3 f5 34. g3 f4 35. Bg2 Bb3 36. Bf3 Kg6 37. gxf4 gxf4 38. h4 Kf5 39. Kh2 Bc2 40. Kh3 Be4 41. Bxe4+ dxe4 42. h5 e3 43. fxe3 $5 fxe3 44. Kg3 Ke4 {Azmaiparashvili,Z (2540)-Romanishin,O (2570)/Tallinn 1988/EXT 2000/ (0-1, 44) Marin,Mihail: 'Azmaiparashvili,Z (2540)-Romanishin,O (2570)/Tallinn 1988/EXT 2000/ (0-1, 44) Marin,M: 'Azmaiparashvili,Z (2540)-Romanishin,O (2570)/Tallinn 1988/EXT 2000/ (0-1, 44)''} 45. h6 Kd3 46. h7 e2 {Marin,M (2557)-Stefansson,H (2557)/ Istanbul 2000/EXT 2001/[Marin,M] (1-0, 58) Marin,Mihail: 'Marin,M (2557)-Stefansson,H (2557)/Istanbul 2000/EXT 2001/[Marin,M] (1-0, 58) Marin,M: 'Marin,M (2557)-Stefansson,H (2557)/ Istanbul 2000/EXT 2001/[Marin,M] (1-0, 58)''} 47. Kf2 Kd2 48. h8=Q e1=Q+ 49. Kg2 Qe2+ 50. Kg1 Qe3+ 51. Kg2 Qxc3 52. Qxc3+ Kxc3 1/2-1/2


