1. e4 {Kritz,Leonid Kritz,Leonid Kritz,Leonid ChessBase Kritz,Leonid: 'Kritz Kritz: 'ChessBase''} e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 Nf6 4. O-O Nxe4 5. d4 Nd6 6. Bxc6 dxc6 7. dxe5 Nf5 8. Qxd8+ Kxd8 9. Nc3 Ke8 10. b3 Bb4 11. Bb2 (11. Ne4 a5 12. a3 Be7 13. a4 Nh4 $11) 11... Bxc3 12. Bxc3 c5 $1 {Before the bishop comes to e6, the squares g5 and d4 must be taken under control by Black.  Bevor der Läufer nach e6 kommt, müssen die Felder g5 und d4 unter Kontrolle genommen werden.} 13. Rad1 h6 $1 14. h3 (14. g4 Ne7 15. h3 h5 16. Nh2 Bd7 17. f4 $6 hxg4 18. hxg4 Rh3 $36) 14... Be6 15. Bb2 b6 16. Rd2 Ne7 17. c4 Nc6 18. Bc3 Ke7 19. Rfd1 a5 20. a4 Rad8 21. Rxd8 Rxd8 22. Rxd8 Kxd8 $15 {Black even has the better of things here, because White's queenside pawns are very frail.  Schwarz steht hier sogar besser, weil die weißen Bauern am Damenflügel sehr anfällig sind.} 23. Kf1 Bf5 24. Ne1 g5 25. Ke2 Ke7 26. Ke3 Ke6 27. f4 g4 28. hxg4 Bxg4 29. Nf3 Bf5 30. Nd2 Ne7 31. Kf3 h5 32. Ne4 Bg4+ 33. Kf2 Nf5 34. Ng5+ Ke7 35. Ne4 Bd1 36. Nd2 Ke6 37. Ke1 Bc2 38. Ke2 Nh4 39. g3 Ng6 40. Kf3 Bd1+ 41. Ke4 Bc2+ 42. Kf3 Kf5 43. Nf1 Bd1+ 44. Kf2 Bxb3 45. Ne3+ Ke4 46. f5 Nxe5 47. Bxe5 Kxe5 48. Nd5 Bxc4 49. Nxc7 Bb3 50. Na8 Bxa4 51. Nxb6 Bb5 52. Ke3 a4 53. Kd2 Kxf5 54. Kc3 Kg4 55. Nd5 Kxg3 56. Nf6 h4 57. Ne4+ Kg2 58. Nxc5 h3 59. Ne4 h2 60. Nd2 h1=Q 61. Kb4 Qe1 62. Kxb5 Qxd2 63. Kxa4 f5 0-1


