1. c4 c5 2. Nf3 b6 3. b3 Bb7 4. Bb2 e6 5. g3 Nf6 6. Bg2 d6 7. O-O Nbd7 8. e3 Be7 9. Qe2 O-O 10. Nc3 Re8 11. Rac1 $5 {[%mdl 4] Exploring less charted territory. Erkundet wenig bekanntes Terrain.} a6 12. Rfd1 Qc7 13. d4 cxd4 14. exd4 Rac8 15. Qe3 $146 ({Predecessor:} 15. Ne1 Bxg2 16. Nxg2 Qb7 17. Ne3 Bf8 18. d5 e5 19. g4 g6 20. g5 Nh5 21. Qg4 {1-0 (45) Vachier Lagrave,M (2778)-Mendonca,L (2472) Chess.com INT 2020}) 15... h6 16. h3 Qb8 17. d5 e5 18. Nh4 Bf8 19. Nf5 Kh7 20. g4 g6 21. Ng3 Bg7 22. Re1 Rcd8 23. Qf3 Kg8 24. h4 Nc5 25. g5 hxg5 26. hxg5 Nh7 27. Nce4 Bc8 28. Rc3 Qc7 29. Bc1 Qe7 30. Nxc5 bxc5 31. Ne4 Bf5 32. Qg3 f6 33. gxf6 Nxf6 34. Bg5 Qf7 35. Bxf6 Bxf6 36. Bh3 Bxh3 37. Qxh3 Bg7 38. Rf3 Qd7 39. Qg2 Rf8 40. Ree3 Rf4 41. Rg3 Qf5 42. Rg5 Qf7 43. Rxg6 Rf8 44. Reg3 Rxe4 45. Rxg7+ Qxg7 46. Rxg7+ Kh8 47. Qxe4 Kxg7 48. Qg4+ Kh6 49. Qe6+ Kg5 50. Qxd6 Rf5 51. Qxc5 e4 52. Qe3+ Kf6 53. Qxe4 a5 54. d6 1-0


