kola Sedlak,Nikola: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'Sedlak,Nikola''} Ng4+ 30. Kh3 Re1 31. Qxd2 Rxg1 32. Kxg4 h5+) 29... Nxf3+ 30. Rxf3 Rd6 $19 {and Black is winning.}) 28. Rxf3 Nxf3+ 29. Qxf3 Re2+ $2 {Sedlak,Nikola: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub: '?'' An unnecessary intermediate move. Sedlak,Nikola: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'An unnecessary intermediate move.''} ({After Sedlak,Nikola: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'After''} 29... Qxf3 {Sedlak,Nikola: '!' '!' '!''Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'Sedlak,Nikola: '!'''} 30. Nxf3 d2 31. Rf1 {Sedlak,Nikola: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub'} (31. Rd1 Rf6 $17 {Sedlak,Nikola: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub: '''} 32. Nd4 {Sedlak,Nikola Sedlak,Nikola: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'Sedlak,Nikola''} (32. Rxd2 {Sedlak,Nikola Sedlak,Nikola: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'Sedlak,Nikola''} Rxf3 $19) 32... Re4 33. Nc2 Re2+ 34. Kg1 Rff2 $19) 31... Re3 $17 {Black is better.}) 30. Kh3 Qxf3 31. Nxf3 Rf6 {Sedlak,Nikola: '!' '!' '!''Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'Sedlak,Nikola: '!'''} 32. Nd4 $2 {Sedlak,Nikola: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub: '?'' This loses the game. Sedlak,Nikola: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'This loses the game.''} ({A much better try was} 32. Rf1 $1 {Sedlak,Nikola: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub'} Kg7 33. Nc3 Re3 34. Kg2 Rc6 35. Nd1 Re2+ 36. Nf2 Rxa2 37. Ne5 Rc3 38. Kh3 $11 {with equality.}) 32... Re4 {Sedlak,Nikola: '-+!' '-+!' '-+!''Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'Sedlak,Nikola: '-+!'''} 33. Nb5 Rf2 $19 {Sedlak,Nikola: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub: '-+''} 34. Nbc3 (34. Rd1 {Sedlak,Nikola: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub'} d2 35. Nbc3 (35. Nac3 Re3) 35... Re3) 34... d2 35. Rb1 Re1 36. Nb2 Rf3 37. Ncd1 $2 {Sedlak,Nikola: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub: '?'' A mistake in a lost position. Sedlak,Nikola: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'A mistake in a lost position.''} (37. Rd1 {Sedlak,Nikola: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub'} Rxc3 38. Rxd2 Rf3) 37... Rg1 38. Kh2 Rfxg3 39. Nc4 R3g2+ 40. Kh3 g5 $1 41. hxg5 Rxg5 42. Kh2 R5g2+ 43. Kh3 Rg6 44. Kh2 R1g2+ 45. Kh3 R2g5 0-1


