{On second board, Jorge Cori had an excellent and aggressive tournament in which he made no draws, something that is quite rare at this level, winning eight games and losing only two. Jorge is on the rise and Baku was a good example of this. Formerly his opening preparation was not up to the standard of play he then shows in the rest of the game, but he has worked hard and, both in this Olympiad and in a number of tournaments in Europe this year, he has made overall progress in this respect. Let’s see his victory in the last round against Howell, a victory that levelled the match against the powerful England team. Sulskis,Sarunas: 'Mareco,Sandro: 'On second board, Jorge Cori had an excellent and aggressive tournament in which he made no draws, something that is quite rare at this level, winning eight games and losing only two. Jorge is on the rise and Baku was a good example of this. Formerly his opening preparation was not up to the standard of play he then shows in the rest of the game, but he has worked hard and, both in this Olympiad and in a number of tournaments in Europe this year, he has made overall progress in this respect. Let’s see his victory in the last round against Howell, a victory that levelled the match against the powerful England team.'' Sulskis,Sarunas: 'Mareco,Sandro: 'On second board, Jorge Cori had an excellent and aggressive tournament in which he made no draws, something that is quite rare at this level, winning eight games and losing only two. Jorge is on the rise and Baku was a good example of this. Formerly his opening preparation was not up to the standard of play he then shows in the rest of the game, but he has worked hard and, both in this Olympiad and in a number of tournaments in Europe this year, he has made overall progress in this respect. Let’s see his victory in the last round against Howell, a victory that levelled the match against the powerful England team.''} 1. e4 {Sulskis,Sarunas Sulskis,Sarunas Sulskis,Sarunas Sulskis,