Bb5 41. d7 Bxd7 42. Rxd7+ $18) 39. Bxc8 {Stohl,Igor: 'Vuckovic,Bojan'} Rxc8 40. Kd3 Rh8 (40... Kf6 41. Re1) 41. Ke4 Re8+ 42. Kf4 Kf6 $11) (37. Re1 {Stohl,Igor} Bc8 $11) (37. Rh7 {Stohl,Igor} Rf7 38. Rxf7+ (38. Rh8 Kg7) 38... Kxf7 39. Bg4 Ke7 40. f4 b5 $11) 37... Bc8 38. f3 $14 {Stohl,Igor: 'Vuckovic,Bojan'} (38. Rh7 {Stohl,Igor} Rf7 39. Rh8 Bf5 $14 {/})) 37. Rh7 Re7 38. Rh8 {Stohl,Igor: 'The h8 is active and the defence is tougher.'} Ke5 $6 {Vuckovic,Bojan: '?' Stohl,Igor: '?' '?' Stohl,Igor: 'Glenn Flear: 'Krasenkow,M: '?!''' Stohl, Igor: '?' Stohl,Igor: 'The decisive error.'} (38... Kg7 $142 {Stohl,Igor: '!' Stohl,Igor: 'Glenn Flear: '' Glenn Flear: 'Krasenkow,M' Vuckovic,Bojan: ''' Stohl, Igor: '!'} 39. Ra8 Kf6 $5 {Stohl,Igor} (39... Bb7 {Stohl,Igor} 40. Rb8 (40. Rxa7 $2 Rf7 41. Bg4 Bxd5 $11) 40... Ba6 41. Bg4 Rf7 $1 42. Re8 (42. d6 Rf8 43. Rxf8 Kxf8 44. Be6 (44. Bd7 g5 45. Kd3 Kf7) 44... Ke8 45. Kd3 Bb7 46. Ke3 g5 $11) 42... Rf4 43. d6 Rxc4+ 44. Kb2 Rb4+ 45. Ka3 Rxg4 46. d7 Rd4 47. d8=Q Rxd8 48. Rxd8 Kf6 49. Rd7 Ke5 50. Rxa7 Bc4 51. Kb2 b5 52. Rg7 Bd3 53. Kc3 Be4 54. Re7+ Kd5 55. a3 Bf5 $14 {is more likely to be a draw - Tablebases show, when Black can afford to play b4.}) 40. Bg4 (40. d6 Rd7 41. Bg4 Rxd6 42. Rxa7 Bxc4 $1 $11) 40... Re4 41. d6 Rxc4+ $14 {leads to the  from the previous line with an extra tempo for Black.}) (38... Rf7 {Vuckovic,Bojan} 39. Re8 $16 {Stohl,Igor: 'Vuckovic,Bojan'} (39. Be4 $1 $16 {Stohl,Igor})) 39. Bg4 $1 {[%cal Rh8g8,Rg8g6] Stohl,Igor: '+-' '+-' Stohl,Igor: 'Glenn Flear: 'Krasenkow,M: '!''' Stohl, Igor: '+-'} b5 $6 {Stohl,Igor: 'Glenn Flear: 'Krasenkow,M: '?!'''} (39... Kd6 {Vuckovic,Bojan} 40. Rg8 $18 {Stohl,Igor: 'Vuckovic,Bojan: '+-''} Re4 {Stohl,Igor} 41. Rxg6+ Ke7 42. Re6+ (42. d6+ $2 Kf7 43. Be6+ Kxg6 44. d7 Bxc4 $11) 42... Rxe6 43. Bxe6 b5 44. a3 $5 bxc4 45. f4 Bb5 (45... Kf6 46. f5 Ke5 47. a4 $22 $18) 46. f5 a5 47. Bc8 Ke8 (47... a4 48. Bb7 $22 Bd7 49. Kxc4 Bxf5 50. Kxc5 Kd8 51. Bc6 Bc2 52. d6 Kc8 53. Kb4 $18) 48. Bb7 $1 (48. d6 $143 Bd7) 48... Ke7 (48... a4 49. Bc6+) 49. Bc6 Ba6 50. a4 $1 Bc8 51. Kxc4 Bxf5 52. Kxc5 Bg4 53. Bb5 $18) 40. Rd8 {Vuckovic,Bojan: '+-!' Stohl,Igor: 'Glenn Flear: 'Threatening d5-d6-d7.'' Stohl,Igor: 'Glenn Flear: 'Threatening d5-d6-d7.' Vuckovic,Bojan: '+-!''} (40. Rf8 $5 $18 {[%cal Rf2f4,Rd5d6] (Stohl,Igor) f4,d6}) 40... Rf7 (40... b4+ {Stohl,Igor} 41. Kd3 Kf4 42. d6 (42. Bc8 $18) 42... Re5 43. Bh3 Rd5+ 44. Kc2 Bxc4 45. Rf8+ Ke5 46. d7 $18) 41. Re8+ Kf4 (41... Kd6 {Stohl,Igor} 42. Re6+) 42. Be6 {Stohl,Igor: 'Glenn Flear: 'There is no stopping the passed d-pawn from going all the way.'' Stohl,Igor: 'The d5 promotes.'} 1-0


