{[%mdl 8192] A21: English Opening: 1...e5 2 Nc3} 1. c4 e5 2. Nc3 Bb4 3. Nd5 Be7 4. d4 d6 5. Nf3 e4 6. Nd2 f5 7. Nb1 Nf6 8. Nbc3 O-O 9. g3 Be6 10. Nxe7+ Qxe7 11. d5 {last book move. White threatens to win material: d5xe6} Bf7 12. Bh3 {White is behind in development.} Ng4 13. Bxg4 fxg4 {Opposite coloured bishops appeared} 14. Be3 {The bishop blocks e4} Nd7 15. Qd4 {White threatens to win material: Qd4xe4} Bg6 16. O-O Rae8 $2 (16... a6 $142 $5 $11 {must be considered}) 17. Qxa7 $16 Qe5 (17... Nc5 18. Bxc5 dxc5 19. e3 $16) 18. Rfc1 (18. Nb5 $142 $5 c6 19. dxc6 bxc6 20. Nxd6 Qxd6 21. Rfd1 $18) 18... Qh5 $16 19. Kf1 $4 {throwing away the advantage} (19. Qd4 $142 $16) 19... Nc5 (19... Qxh2 $6 20. Ke1 Nc5 21. Kd2 Rxf2 22. Rh1 Qxg3 23. Rag1 $15) 20. Qa3 $4 {strolling merrily down the path to disaster} (20. b4 $142 Qxh2 21. Ke1 $17) 20... Qxh2 $19 21. Ke1 Ra8 22. Qb4 (22. Kd2 {is no salvation} Rxa3 23. Rh1 Qg2 $19) 22... Nd3+ 23. exd3 (23. Kd2 {there is nothing else anyway} Nxb4 24. Rh1 Rxf2 25. Rxh2 Rxh2 26. Rg1 $19) 23... Qg1+ 24. Kd2 Rxf2+ 25. Ne2 (25. Bxf2 {is still a small chance} Qxf2+ 26. Ne2 exd3 27. a4 Qxe2+ 28. Kc3 $19) 25... Rxe2+ 26. Kxe2 Qg2+ 27. Kd1 exd3 28. Qe1 Rf8 29. Bf4 Re8 (29... Be4 $142 {ends the debate} 30. Qxe4 Qxe4 $19) 30. Be3 $17 Rf8 {Twofold repetition} 31. Bf4 Be4 32. Rc3 (32. Qxe4 {is not the saving move} Qxe4 33. Kd2 $19) 32... Re8 (32... g5 $142 {and the result of the game is clear: Black will win} 33. Rxd3 Bxd3 34. Qe6+ Rf7 $19) 33. Kc1 Bg6 {Black has a mate threat} 34. Qd1 $4 {gives the opponent counterplay} (34. Be3 $142 $5 $11 {is a viable option}) 34... Re2 $17 35. Bd2 $2 (35. b4 h5 36. Bd2 h4 37. gxh4 g3 $19) 35... Rf2 (35... h5 36. b3 $19) 36. b3 $2 (36. Be1 Rf1 37. b4 h5 $11) 36... Be4 (36... Qxg3 $142 37. c5 dxc5 $19) 37. Qxg4 $4 {causes further problems for White} (37. Be1 $142 Bf3 38. Qxd3 $17) 37... Rf1+ $19 (37... Rxd2 $6 {is impossible} 38. Qe6+ Kf8 39. Qc8+ Kf7 40. Qe6+ (40. Qxc7+ {leads to a pleasing mate} Kg6 41. Qxd6+ Kh5 42. Qe5+ g5 43. Qe8+ Bg6 44. g4+ Kxg4 45. Qe6+ Bf5 46. Qe1 Rc2+ 47. Kb1 Rb2+ 48. Kc1 d2+ 49. Kxb2 dxe1=Q+ 50. Ka3 Qxc3 51. Ka4 Bd7+ 52. Ka3 Qgb2#) 40... Kf8 41. Qc8+ Kf7 42. Qe6+ Kf8 $11) 38. Kb2 Qxd2+ 39. Ka3 Bf5 (39... Rxa1 $6 {is a weaker possibility} 40. Qe6+ Kf8 41. Qc8+ Ke7 42. Qe6+ Kf8 43. Qc8+ Ke7 44. Qe6+ Kf8 $11) 40. Qh4 (40. Qh5 {praying for a miracle} g6 41. Qh4 Rxa1 42. Qd8+ Kf7 43. Kb4 $19) 40... Rxa1 (40... Rxa1 41. Qd8+ Kf7 42. Qxc7+ Kg6 43. Qxd6+ Kh5 44. g4+ Kxg4 45. Kb4 Qxa2 46. Qc7 Qa3+ 47. Kb5 g5 48. c5 Qa6+ 49. Kb4 d2 50. Rg3+ Kh5 51. Rh3+ Bxh3 52. Qxh7+ Kg4 53. Qe4+ Kg3 54. Qe3+ Kh4 55. Qd4+ Kh5 56. Qh8+ Kg4 57. Qd4+ Kf5 58. Kc3 d1=N+ 59. Qxd1 Rxd1 60. c6 Qa1+ 61. Kb4 Qd4+ 62. Ka5 Ra1+ 63. Kb5 Bf1#) 0-1


