1. Nf3 Nf6 2. c4 g6 3. Nc3 d5 4. Qa4+ Bd7 5. Qb3 dxc4 6. Qxc4 a6 7. e4 b5 8. Qe2 Bc8 9. d4 (9. e5 {Ü 80/11}) 9... Bg7 10. g3 c5 $6 $146 (10... Bb7) (10... b4) 11. dxc5 (11. Bg2 cxd4 12. Nxd4 e5 13. Nf3 Nc6 $13) 11... O-O 12. Bg2 Be6 13. e5 Nfd7 $6 (13... Nd5 $145 14. Nd4 Nxc3 15. Nxe6 $1 (15. bxc3 $6 Bc4 16. Qe3 Bd5 17. O-O Bxg2 18. Kxg2 Qd5+ 19. Qf3 Qxf3+ 20. Nxf3 Nd7 $11) 15... Nxe2 16. Nxd8 Nxc1 17. Bxa8 (17. Rxc1 $5 Ra7 18. Nb7 Bxe5 19. b4 $14) 17... Nd3+ 18. Ke2 Nxb2 19. Nc6 Nxc6 20. Bxc6 Rc8 21. Bb7 $16 {Svidler,P}) 14. O-O Nxc5 15. Rd1 Nbd7 16. Nd4 Bc4 17. Qe3 Nxe5 (17... Rc8 18. Nc6 $16) 18. Nc6 Nxc6 19. Rxd8 Raxd8 20. Qxc5 Bxc3 21. Bxc6 (21. h4 $145 $1 Rd1+ 22. Kh2 Ne5 (22... Bd4 23. Qxc6 Bxf2 24. Bf3 $18) 23. bxc3 Ng4+ 24. Kh3 Be6 25. f3 (25. Bf3 $5 Nxf2+ 26. Kh2 Nd3 27. Qe3 Rxc1 28. Rxc1 Nxc1 29. Qxc1 $18) 25... Nf2+ 26. Kh2 Nd3 27. Qe3 Rd8 28. a3 $18 {Svidler,P}) 21... Rd1+ 22. Kg2 Bf6 $1 23. Bb7 Bf1+ 24. Kf3 Rfd8 25. Be4 Re1 26. Qc2 Bg7 27. g4 h5 28. gxh5 f5 (28... gxh5 29. Rb1 $18) 29. Bb7 gxh5 30. Qc7 $6 (30. a4 $1 Bd3 31. Qc5 Be2+ 32. Kg2 Bf1+ 33. Kg3 f4+ 34. Bxf4 Rxa1 35. Qxe7 $18) 30... Be2+ 31. Kg3 $6 (31. Kg2 $1 Bf1+ 32. Kg3 Be5+ 33. Qxe5 Rxe5 34. Bf4 $16) 31... Rg1+ 32. Bg2 (32. Kf4 Rd4+ $1 33. Ke3 Bg4 34. f3 Bh3 35. Qc8+ Kh7 36. Qe8 f4+ 37. Ke2 Rg2+ $11) 32... Rd3+ 33. Be3 Rxa1 $2 (33... h4+ $145 $1 34. Kh3 (34. Kxh4 $2 Rxg2 35. Qxe7 Rg6 $17) 34... Bg4+ 35. Kxh4 Rxg2 36. Qxe7 Rd5 $1 37. Rc1 Bf3 38. Kh3 Rg4 (38... f4 39. Rc8+ Kh7 40. Qh4+ Rh5 41. Qxh5+ Bxh5 42. Kxg2 fxe3 43. fxe3 Bxb2 44. Ra8 $11) 39. Qe8+ Kh7 40. Qh5+ $11 {Svidler,P}) 34. Qc8+ Kf7 35. Qxf5+ Bf6 36. h4 $6 (36. Bf3 $1 Rg1+ 37. Kf4 Bf1 38. Bd5+ Kg7 39. Qxh5 Rxd5 40. Qxd5 Bg5+ 41. Qxg5+ Rxg5 42. Kxg5 $14) 36... Rxe3+ $6 (36... Kg7 $1 37. Be4 Rxe3+ $1 38. fxe3 Rg1+ 39. Kh2 Rg4 $13) 37. fxe3 Bg4 (37... Kg7 $142) 38. Qh7+ Bg7 39. Be4 $2 (39. Bf3 $1 Kf8 40. Bxg4 Rg1+ 41. Kf2 Rxg4 42. Qxh5 $18) 39... Kf8 40. Bg6 Rxa2 41. Bxh5 Bxh5 42. Qxh5 Rxb2 {[ 5/i]} 43. Qf5+ Bf6 44. e4 Rc2 45. h5 Rc3+ 46. Kg2 Rc2+ 47. Kf3 Rc3+ 48. Ke2 b4 49. h6 Rc2+ 50. Ke3 Rh2 51. Qg6 b3 52. h7 Bg7 53. e5 Rh6 54. Qf5+ Ke8 55. Kd2 $1 e6 56. Qe4 Kf7 (56... b2 57. Kc2 Rh2+ 58. Kb1 Ke7 59. Ka2 $1 a5 60. Kb1 $1) 57. Kc3 Rh5 58. Kxb3 Rxe5 59. Qh4 Rd5 60. h8=Q Bxh8 61. Qxh8 {[ 2/i]} a5 62. Kc4 Rf5 63. Kd4 Rd5+ 64. Ke4 Rf5 65. Qh7+ Ke8 66. Qg7 Rd5 67. Qf6 Kd7 68. Qf7+ Kd6 69. Qe8 Re5+ 70. Kf4 Rf5+ 71. Kg4 Ke5 72. Qd8 a4 (72... Ke4 73. Qd6 Re5 74. Kg3 Rg5+ 75. Kh4 Re5 76. Kg4) 73. Qa5+ Kf6 74. Qxa4 {[ 2/e]} Ke7 75. Qa7+ Kd6 76. Qb8+ Kd7 77. Qb7+ Kd6 78. Qc8 Ke7 79. Qc7+ Ke8 80. Qd6 Kf7 81. Qd7+ Kf6 82. Qe8 Rg5+ 83. Kh4 Rf5 84. Qf8+ Kg6 85. Qe7 Re5 86. Kg4 Re4+ 87. Kf3 Re1 88. Qh4 Re5 89. Qe7 Re1 90. Kf4 Rf1+ 91. Ke5 Re1+ 92. Kd6 Rd1+ 93. Kc6 Re1 94. Qh4 Re5 95. Kd6 Rh5 96. Qe4+ Kg7 97. Kxe6 {[ 2/a]} Rh6+ 98. Ke7 Rg6 99. Qd4+ Kg8 100. Qe5 Rg1 101. Qd5+ Kh7 102. Qd3+ Kg8 103. Kf6 Rg7 104. Qd5+ Kh7 105. Qh1+ Kg8 106. Qh5 Ra7 107. Qd5+ 1-0


