1. e4 e5 2. f4 exf4 3. Bc4 d6 (3... Qh4+ 4. Kf1 d6 5. d4 $5 Nc6 6. Nc3 Bg4 7. Qd2 g5 8. g3 {<xml:en>transposes to the game.</:en/xml>}) 4. d4 (4. Nf3 {<xml:en>is a good alternative here, leading back into mainline theory.</:en/xml>}) 4... Qh4+ 5. Kf1 {<xml:en>Black has a number of options here:</:en/xml>} Nc6 (5... Be6 6. Qd3 (6. d5 Bg4 7. Nf3 $10) (6. Bxe6 fxe6 7. Nf3 Qf6 8. Qd2 Nc6 9. Nc3 O-O-O 10. d5 exd5 11. exd5 Ne5 12. Qxf4 $10) 6... Nf6 7. Nf3 Qg4 8. Nc3 Be7 9. h3 Qg6 10. Bxf4 O-O 11. Re1 Nh5 12. Bh2 Ng3+ 13. Bxg3 Qxg3 14. Ne2 Qg6 15. Nf4 Qh6 16. g3 Nd7 17. Kg2 Nb6 18. Bxe6 fxe6 19. Rhf1 c5 20. d5 Rxf4 21. gxf4 Qxf4 22. dxe6 Rf8 23. b4 Rf6 24. Qb5 Rxe6 25. bxc5 Bh4 26. Nxh4 Qxh4 27. Qb3 d5 28. cxb6 {1-0 (28) Ivanchuk,V (2716)-Nikolic,P (2648) Antalya 2004}) (5... Bg4 6. Qd2 $1 g5 7. g3 fxg3 8. Nc3 $1 Nc6 {back into the main game.}) (5... Nf6 6. Nc3 Ng4 $5 7. Qe2 (7. Nh3) 7... Nxh2+ 8. Rxh2 Qxh2 9. Nd5 Kd8 10. Bxf4 Qh1 11. Kf2 c6 12. Nc3 Kc7 13. Rd1 {<xml:en>with compensation but Black is probably better.</:en/xml>}) 6. Nc3 Bg4 7. Qd2 $1 {[%draw arrow,g2,g3] [%draw arrow,f1,g2]} g5 8. g3 fxg3 $2 (8... Qh5 9. gxf4 gxf4 10. Nd5 O-O-O 11. Nxf4 Qh6 12. Qg2 $1 $10) 9. Kg2 Qh5 10. hxg3 Qg6 11. Qxg5 $6 (11. Nh3 $1 Be7 12. Nf2 $1 Bd7 13. Nd5 Bd8 14. b4 $14) 11... Nxd4 12. Qxg6 fxg6 13. Bxg8 Rxg8 14. Nd5 O-O-O (14... Nxc2 $1 15. Rb1 (15. Nxc7+ Kd7 16. Nxa8 Nxa1 17. Rxh7+ Rg7 18. Rh4 Be6 $15)) 15. Bg5 Re8 16. Rxh7 $14 Rg7 $2 (16... Ne6 17. Be3 Bg7 18. Rh4 Bh5 19. Rf1 {[%draw full,h5]}) 17. Rh8 $16 Rf7 18. Nf6 Re5 19. Bh6 $2 (19. Be3 $1 Nxc2 20. Nxg4 Rxe4 21. Rf1 $1 Rxf1 22. Kxf1 Rxg4 23. Rxf8+ Kd7 24. Bf2 $16) 19... Rxf6 20. Bxf8 Re8 21. Bg7 Rxh8 22. Bxh8 Nxc2 23. Bxf6 Nxa1 24. Nf3 Be6 (24... Nc2 $15 {[%draw full,f6] [%draw full,g4]}) 25. a3 c5 26. Nh4 Bf7 27. Kf3 Kd7 28. Kf4 Nb3 29. Bc3 c4 30. Nf3 Nc5 31. Ke3 a6 32. Bd4 Ne6 33. Bf6 Be8 34. Ng5 Nc5 35. Kd4 b5 36. e5 Na4 37. Kd5 Nb6+ 38. Kd4 Na4 39. Kd5 dxe5 40. Bxe5 a5 41. Bd4 Ke7 42. Nf3 Bf7+ 43. Kc6 Be8+ 1/2-1/2


