. Be2 Qxf4+ 29. Kd3 Nxe2 30. Rxe2 Qxf3+) 28... Nxh1 29. Rxh1 Qxf4+ 30. Kc2 Qxf3 31. exd6 cxd6) 27... Qxf4+ 28. Kf2 Qd2+ $1 29. Be2 ({Fischer,Johannes: 'After'} 29. Kxg3 Rg8+ {Fischer,Johannes: 'White has to give his queen to avoid mate.'}) 29... Nxe4+ 30. fxe4 Rf8+ 31. Kg3 Bc8 $1 0-1


