1. d4 Nf6 2. Nf3 d5 3. c4 e6 4. Nc3 Nbd7 5. cxd5 exd5 6. Bf4 c6 7. e3 Nh5 8. Bd3 Nxf4 9. exf4 Bd6 (9... Qe7+ $6 {- 74/(424)}) 10. g3 O-O 11. O-O Re8 12. Qc2 Nf8 13. Rfe1 $146 (13. Nd1) 13... Rxe1+ 14. Rxe1 Bd7 15. f5 Qf6 16. Ne5 (16. Nd1 $5) 16... Re8 17. f4 Qd8 $1 $36 18. Qb3 Qb6 (18... Bc8 $5) 19. Qxb6 axb6 20. Kf2 Ra8 21. a4 (21. Nxd7 Nxd7 22. a4 Kf8 $11) 21... Bc8 22. Bc2 Nd7 23. Kf3 Kf8 24. g4 f6 (24... Nf6 $5) 25. Nd3 (25. Nxd7+ Bxd7 $36) 25... Nb8 $5 26. b4 $11 Na6 27. Rb1 Nc7 28. Ne2 $6 (28. b5 $1 Rb8 $11) 28... Bd7 29. Ng3 Be7 $1 $15 {[ e8-d6]} 30. h4 Ne8 31. h5 h6 (31... Kf7 $5) 32. Ne2 Nd6 33. Nb2 b5 $1 34. a5 $6 (34. Ra1) 34... Ne4 $17 35. Bxe4 dxe4+ 36. Kxe4 Bxb4 37. Nd3 Re8+ (37... Bxa5 $142 38. Nc5 Bc8 39. Ra1 Kf7 $17) 38. Kf3 Bxa5 39. Nc5 Bc8 40. d5 $1 Bb6 41. Ne6+ Bxe6 (41... Ke7 $5) 42. fxe6 (42. dxe6 $6 Rd8 $17) 42... Rd8 43. Ng3 $5 (43. dxc6 bxc6 44. Rb3 Ke7 45. f5 $15) 43... Rxd5 44. Nf5 Bc5 $8 45. Ra1 Rd8 46. g5 $5 (46. Rc1 Be7 47. Rb1 $15) 46... fxg5 47. fxg5 hxg5 48. h6 gxh6 49. Rh1 Rd5 $1 50. Kg4 Re5 $2 (50... Ke8 $1 51. Rxh6 Kd8 $1 52. Rh8+ Kc7 53. e7 Bxe7 54. Nxe7 Rd1 $17) 51. Rxh6 $11 Kg8 52. Rg6+ Kh7 53. Rh6+ Kg8 54. Rg6+ Kh7 55. Rh6+ Kg8 1/2-1/2


