t the white quee'(RR) (Marjanovic,Slavoljub) going to f5. Now the position after Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'going to f5. Now the position after Mikhalevski, V: 'going to f5. Now the position after Neil McDonald: ', trying to exploit the white queen by putting the knight on f5, White got the edge in D.Stellwagen-V.Erdos, Remagen 2011, with'''' n by putting the knight on f5, White got the edge in D.Stellwagen-V.Erdos, Remagen 2011, with'} 14. c5 Nf5 15. Qf4 Rb8 {requires deep investigation.} 16. Ne4 {Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub'} d6 17. Nxf6+ Qxf6 18. Qc4+ Qf7 19. Qxf7+ Rxf7 20. b3 $1 {as the black queenside pawns are mouldy.}) (13... d6 {RR: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub'} 14. Be3 (14. Ne4 Bf5 15. Bg5) 14... Be6 15. Ng5 Bf5 (15... Bxc4 16. Qh4 Bd3 17. Red1) 16. Nce4) 14. Bg5 $1 {The initiative is more imp'RR: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'Mikhalevski, V: '!' Mikhalevski, V: 'The initiative is more important than a pawn here.'' Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'Mikhalevski, V: '!' '!' Mikhalevski, V: 'The initiative is more important than a pawn here.'''' ortant than a pawn here.} Nd3 $2 {After this move Black finds himself'RR: '?' RR: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub: '?!' '?!' '?!' Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'Mikhalevski, V: '?' Mikhalevski, V: 'After this move Black finds himself on the edge of a precipice.'' Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'Mikhalevski, V: '?' '?' Mikhalevski, V: 'After this move Black finds himself on the edge of a precipice.'''' on the edge of a precipice. Marjanovic,Slavoljub: '?!' RR: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub: '?!' '?!' Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'Mikhalevski, V: '?' Mikhalevski, V: 'After this move Black finds himself on the edge of a precipice.'''} ({Neil McDonald: 'As his knight raid ends'RR: 'Geboten ist Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'Mikhalevski, V: 'Neil McDonald: 'As his knight raid ends in disaster, Black should have thought about development with ''''' in disaster, Black should have thought about development with '} 14... d6 {was necessary. Neil McDonal'RR: 'Marjanovic,Slavoljub: 'Mikhale