1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 g6 5. Nc3 (5. c4 Nf6 6. Nc3 Nxd4 7. Qxd4 d6 8. Be2 Bg7 9. Be3 O-O 10. Qd2) 5... Bg7 6. Be3 Nf6 7. Be2 (7. Bc4 O-O 8. Bb3 Ng4 (8... Na5 9. e5 Ne8 10. Bxf7+ Kxf7 11. Ne6) 9. Qxg4 Nxd4 10. Qd1 (10. Qh4)) 7... O-O (7... d5 8. Bb5) 8. f4 (8. O-O d5 9. exd5 Nb4) 8... d6 (8... d5 9. e5 Ne4 10. Nxe4 dxe4 11. Nxc6 bxc6 12. Qxd8 Rxd8 13. Bc4) 9. Nb3 Be6 (9... a5 10. a4 Be6 11. Nd4 (11. g4 Nb4) (11. O-O Rc8) 11... Qb6 $17 {Wang,A (2288)-Niemann,H (2329) Charlotte 2018} 12. Nxe6 Qxe3 13. Nxf8 Ng4) 10. g4 d5 11. f5 Bc8 ({Keeping the pin with} 11... gxf5 $2 {would be bad now, as}) 12. exd5 Nb4 13. Bf3 $6 (13. d6 Qxd6 (13... exd6 $15 {Turner,M (2521)-Adams,M (2735) England 2012} 14. g5 $5) 14. Bc5 Qf4 15. Rf1 Qxh2 16. Bxb4 Nxg4 17. Bxg4 Qg3+ 18. Rf2 Qg1+) (13. fxg6 $5 {is a completely playable alternative.} hxg6 14. Bf3 Bxg4 15. Bxg4 Nxg4 16. Qxg4 Nxc2+ 17. Kf2 Nxa1 {(Michiels,B (2506)-Steingrimsson,H (2543) Warsaw 2013)} 18. Rxa1 $5 Rc8 19. Bd4 $132 Rc4 $5) 13... gxf5 14. a3 fxg4 $6 15. Bg2 (15. axb4 gxf3 16. Qxf3 {Thanks for the d4 isolated pawn Black's position is more comfortable.} Bg4) 15... Na6 16. Qd3 (16. Qe2 Bf5) 16... e6 (16... Nd7 17. O-O-O Ne5 18. Qe2) 17. O-O-O (17. d6 Nd5 18. Bxd5 $14 {Maletin,P (2584)-Giri,A (2690) Olginka 2011} {Probably} exd5 $5 {was the most accurate followed by the quick ...c8 queenside's play.} 19. Qxd5 $5 {is the other option.} Re8) 17... Nxd5 (17... exd5 18. h3 g3 19. Bd4) 18. h3 g3 19. Rhg1 Qd6 20. Bxd5 exd5 21. Nxd5 (21. Bd4 Bxd4 22. Rxg3+ Bg7 (22... Kh8 23. Qxd4+ f6 24. Rf3) 23. Rdg1 Qh6+ 24. Kb1 Be6 25. Rxg7+ Qxg7 26. Rxg7+ Kxg7 27. Qg3+ Kh8 $11 (27... Kf6 28. Qd6 Kg7 29. Nxd5) 28. Qe5+ $5 Kg8 29. Qg5+ Kh8 {/=} 30. Qf6+ Kg8 31. Ne2) 21... Kh8 22. Bf4 (22. Bd4 Bxd4 (22... f6 23. Rxg3 Qxd5 24. Bxf6) 23. Qxd4+ f6) 22... Qg6 23. Qd2 (23. Qf3 Bf5 24. Rxg3 Qc6) 23... Bxh3 24. Rxg3 Bg4 25. Rh1 $14 Rfe8 26. Ne3 Qe4 (26... Qf6 27. Nxg4 Qxb2+ 28. Kd1 Rad8 29. Rd3) (26... f5 27. Qh2 Kg8) 27. Qh2 Be6 (27... Bf5 28. Rxg7 Kxg7 29. Nxf5+ Qxf5 30. Nd4) 28. Rxg7 (28. Nd2) 28... Kxg7 29. Qh6+ Kg8 (29... Kh8 30. Be5+) 30. Rg1+ Qg6 31. Rxg6+ fxg6 32. Nd4 Rad8 33. Be5 Rd7 34. Nxe6 Rxe6 35. Ng4 Rf7 36. Qg5 Rf1+ 37. Kd2 h5 38. Qd8+ (38. Qd8+ Rf8 39. Nh6+) 1/2-1/2


