1. c4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 e6 6. Bf4 d5 7. e3 Bb4 8. Be2 dxc4 9. Nxc6 Qxd1+ 10. Rxd1 (10. Kxd1 bxc6 11. Bxc4 Nd5 12. Kc2 Bxc3 (12... Nxf4 13. exf4 Bb7 $11) 13. bxc3 Nxf4 14. exf4 Rb8 15. Rhe1 Ke7 16. Re5 Rd8 17. Ra5 $14 {½-½ (32) Gordon,S (2496)-Swapnil,S (2499) Bangkok 2016}) 10... bxc6 11. Bxc4 (11. Be5 Nd5 (11... Nd7 12. Bd6 Bxd6 13. Rxd6 Bb7 $11 14. Bxc4 $6 Nb6 15. Be2 Nd5 {[%csl Rd6] and White should start worrying about his rook.}) 12. e4 Nxc3 13. bxc3 f6 14. Bxf6 gxf6 15. cxb4 $14 {1-0 (110) Zhang,Z (2619)-Ponomariov,R (2710) Berlin 2015}) (11. O-O Nd5 12. Ne4 Nxf4 13. exf4 Ke7 14. a3 Ba5 15. Bxc4 Rd8 $11 {0-1 (35) Payen,A (2346)-Korpa,B (2474) Budapest 2016}) 11... Nd5 12. Bg3 $1 {The only attempt to pose some problems for Black. White is allowing him to take a pawn with check!} (12. O-O Bxc3 (12... Nxf4 13. exf4 Ke7 14. Ne4 Rb8 15. Rd3 Ba5 16. b3 Rd8 $11 {½-½ (56) Yilmaz,M (2622)-Salgado Lopez,I (2651) Izmir 2016}) (12... Nxc3 13. bxc3 Bxc3 14. Bd6 a5 {[%cal Gc3b4] is another possible idea, which should be sufficient for equality.}) 13. bxc3 Nxf4 14. exf4 Ke7 15. Rb1 (15. Rfe1 Rb8 16. f5 Rd8 17. Rxd8 Kxd8 18. fxe6 Bxe6 19. Bxe6 fxe6 $11 {½-½ (31) Wei,Y (2700)-Zhou,W (2635) Xinghua 2016}) 15... Bd7 16. Rb7 Rhb8 17. Rfb1 Rxb7 18. Rxb7 a5 19. Bd3 h6 20. h4 Kd8 21. Kf1 Kc8 22. Rb1 Rb8 $11 {½-½ (30) Carlsen,M (2872)-Kramnik,V (2810) London 2013}) 12... Nxc3 13. bxc3 Bxc3+ 14. Ke2 O-O 15. Rd3 Bf6 $6 (15... Ba5 $1 {was the right route for the bishop.} 16. Rhd1 Bb6 {White has full compensation for the pawn, but hardly more than that.}) 16. Rb1 {Now White controls both open files and the position is becoming unpleasant for Black.} Rd8 17. Bd6 e5 18. e4 a5 19. Rb6 Ra7 20. f3 Be6 21. Bxe6 fxe6 22. Bb8 Rxd3 23. Kxd3 Rd7+ 24. Kc3 Rd1 25. Rb2 Kf7 26. Bc7 a4 27. Kb4 Rd4+ 28. Kc3 Rd1 29. Rc2 Ke7 30. Bb6 Bg5 31. Bc5+ Kd7 32. Kb4 Be7 33. Bxe7 Kxe7 34. Kxa4 Kd6 35. Kb3 c5 36. a4 Kc6 37. Ra2 Rd3+ 38. Kc2 Rd4 39. a5 Kb7 40. a6+ Ka7 41. Ra5 Rc4+ 42. Kd2 g5 43. g4 h6 44. h3 Rd4+ 45. Kc3 Rd1 46. Rxc5 Ra1 47. Rxe5 Rxa6 48. Kd4 Kb7 49. h4 Kc7 50. hxg5 1-0


